    "body": "### Problem\n\n- https://github.com/kevinhwang91/nvim-bqf/issues/112#issuecomment-1582145219\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\n**minimal_init.lua**\r\n\r\n```lua\r\nlocal function dir(root)\r\n  local f = debug.getinfo(1, \"S\").source:sub(2)\r\n  return vim.fn.fnamemodify(f, \":p:h\") .. \"/\" .. (root or \"\")\r\nend\r\n\r\nvim.cmd([[set runtimepath=$VIMRUNTIME]])\r\nvim.opt.runtimepath:append(dir())\r\nvim.opt.packpath = { dir(\".repro/site\") }\r\nvim.env.XDG_CONFIG_HOME = dir(\".repro/config\")\r\nvim.env.XDG_DATA_HOME = dir(\".repro/data\")\r\nvim.env.XDG_STATE_HOME = dir(\".repro/state\")\r\nvim.env.XDG_CACHE_HOME = dir(\".repro/cache\")\r\n\r\nvim.o.number = true\r\nvim.o.scrolloff = 5\r\nvim.o.splitbelow = true\r\nvim.o.splitkeep = \"screen\"\r\n\r\nvim.cmd(\"vimgrep v %\")\r\n\r\nlocal o_winid = vim.api.nvim_get_current_win()\r\n\r\nvim.cmd(\"copen\")\r\n\r\nlocal qf_winid = vim.api.nvim_get_current_win()\r\n\r\nvim.api.nvim_create_autocmd(\"CursorMoved\", {\r\n  callback = function()\r\n    vim.cmd(\"noa call nvim_set_current_win(\" .. o_winid .. \")\")\r\n    vim.cmd(\"noa call nvim_set_current_win(\" .. qf_winid .. \")\")\r\n  end,\r\n})\r\n```\r\n\r\n- `nvim -u NORC -u minimal_init.lua minimal_init.lua`\r\n- Try to move cursor down in the quickfix window\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nShould be able to move cursor up and down normally.\n\n### Neovim version (nvim -v)\n\nNVIM v0.10.0-dev-1768+gc48f94d1f-Homebrew\n\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\n\nnot sure\n\n### Operating system/version\n\nmacOS 13.4\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\nKitty\n\n### $TERM environment variable\n\ntmux-256color\n\n### Installation\n\nhomebrew",
